(Wed 26th Session 2), at the workshop <a href='https://www.hamlynsymposium.org/events/endoluminal-robots-a-journey-from-unmet-medical-needs-design-challenges-regulatory-bodies-and-commercial-opportunities-2nd-edition/'> Endoluminal Robots </a>!,
and the ISMR workshop <a href='https://ismr.gatech.edu/sites/default/files/pdfs/Detailed%20Program_2024.pdf/'>The Third Holistic Forum of Medical Robotic Junior Professors </a>!.

Reach out to meet if you are attending these conferences!
